{"tid":225273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】警無線電干擾空管通訊錄音公開","createTime":"2017-05-01T16:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T21:38:59.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b334506b74467d8610fa6285d5e55364f779bdd","tid":225273,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82tYN4uZ10Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D82tYN4uZ10Y&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=97eee0d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82tYN4uZ10Y</a><br />\n<br />\n《香港01》接獲相關的空管人員錄音，當時正值昨午大約2時，剛好是佐科維多多乘坐航班抵港的時間，在錄音大約20分鐘中可以聽到「沙沙聲響」。機場發展關注網絡發言人巫堃泰表示，錄音當中的「沙沙聲響」就是無線電干擾車正干擾的證據：「平時係唔會有呢啲咁嘅聲，同埋當時好明顯係佐科維多多架機已經抵港，架無線電干擾車就喺禁區附近，所以就會有干擾嘅情況出現。」<br />\n<br />\n他續指，如此的情況會對停機坪的交通有所大影響：「佢咁樣干擾會令到空管人員作唔到指令，航班有機會延誤、亦可能會令機師聽錯指令，又或者喺停機坪嘅飛機，因為聽唔到指令而撞向禁區嘅旅遊巴，所以真係可以好危險！」記者在今（1日）午佐科維多多離境時，再聆聽空管人員的錄音，但就沒有如昨日的「沙沙聲響」。"},{"pid":"a210010bfed39da36cfe5192d0b86c023bdd1e00","tid":225273,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"負皮系畀香港01既"},{"pid":"12765f8679e5e50677384c84d196974dbdda7f0f","tid":225273,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"HK01重神秘過大帽山"},{"pid":"8ebbccb5a1e3582c40d2ae981d4a5b10894d6184","tid":225273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HK01重神秘過大帽山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGround Control to Major Tom<br />\nGround Control to Major Tom<br />\nTake your protein pills and put your helmet on<br />\nGround Control to Major Tom (ten, nine, eight, seven, six)<br />\nCommencing countdown, engines on (five, four, three)<br />\nCheck ignition and may God's love be with you (two, one, liftoff)"},{"pid":"22ea236d2bb62c3a40bb69767f70b75c2deae2bf","tid":225273,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy